Class TestFruitPairGenerator

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.abc.ds.keyvalue.tests.TestFruitPairGenerator
  • public class TestFruitPairGenerator
extends java.lang.Object
    Used to produce key-value pairs with the fruit as a key and a string-length of the fruit name formatted as a string as the value. For example: key="apple" value="5"
